					<h1 id="get-started">Getting Started</h1>


					<h2 class="text-left">1. Include Social Sharing on your site.</h2>

					<pre><code class="language-markup">&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="css/social-sharing-css.css"&gt;</code></pre>

					<p>If you're <em>not</em> using the <a href="http://cferdinandi.github.io/kraken/">Kraken boilerplate</a>, you might also need to include the button styling.</p>

					<pre><code class="language-markup">&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="kraken-buttons.css"&gt;</code></pre>

					<p>Social Sharing is <a href="http://sass-lang.com/">built with Sass</a> for easy customization. If you don't use Sass, that's ok. The <code>css</code> folder contains compiled vanilla CSS.</p>

					<p>The <code>_config.scss</code> and <code>_mixins.scss</code> files are the same ones used in <a href="http://cferdinandi.github.io/kraken/">Kraken</a>, so you can drop the <code>_social-sharing.css</code> file right into Kraken without making any updates. Or, adjust the variables to suit your own project.</p>


					<h2 class="text-left">2. Add the markup to your HTML.</h2>

					<p>A few simple classes turn <code class="language-markup">button</code> and <code class="language-markup">a</code> elements into branded social media buttons.</p>

<pre><code class="language-markup">&lt;a class="btn btn-tweet" href="#"&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-facebook" href="#"&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-google" href="#"&gt;Google+&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-linkedin" href="#"&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-pinterest" href="#"&gt;Pinterest&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-github" href="#"&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-vk" href="#"&gt;VK&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="btn btn-xing" href="#"&gt;Xing&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>

					<p>To include sharing links for Twitter, Facebook, Google+, LinkedIn and Pinterest, just add your URL's and titles where indicated in these snippets. Combine with the branded buttons for sharing buttons.</p>

<pre><code class="language-markup">&lt;a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=YOUR-TITLE&url=YOUR-URL&via=TWITTER-HANDLE"&gt;Tweet&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=YOUR-URL"&gt;Share on Facebook&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a target="_blank" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=YOUR-URL"&gt;Plus on Google+&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=YOUR-URL&title=YOUR-TITLE&summary=YOUR-SUMMARY&source=YOUR-URL"&gt;Share on LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=YOUR-URL&description=YOUR-DESCRIPTION&media=YOUR-IMAGE-SRC"&gt;Pin on Pinterest&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a target="_blank" href="https://vk.com/share.php?url=YOUR-URL&title=YOUR-TITLE&description=YOUR-DESCRIPTION&image=YOUR-IMAGE-SRC&noparse=true"&gt;Share on VK&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a target="_blank" href="https://www.xing-share.com/app/user?op=share;sc_p=xing-share;url=YOUR-URL"&gt;Share on Xing&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>


					<h2 class="text-left">3. Pat yourself on the back.</h2>

					<p>Seriously, you're done. Nice work! Modify as needed.</p>

